Package: gateway
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Working with St. Louis Spatial Data
Version: 0.3.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Christopher", "Prener", ,"chris.prener@slu.edu", c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4310-9888")),
    person("Branson", "Fox", ,"branson.fox@slu.edu", c("aut"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4361-2811"))
    )
Description: Contains various tools for accessing and modifying spatial data for the
    City of St. Louis, Missouri. These include tools for downloading data about the city,
    a composite geocoder for returning the latitude and longitude of street addresses, and
    tools for locating addresses within neighborhoods, tracts, and other geometries (known
    as spatial joins).
